---
// apps/pmg/src/components/FAQ.astro
---

<!-- FAQ Section -->
<section id="faq" class="section scroll-mt bg-navy-mid-blur">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-tag">Information</span>
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">
      Get clear insights about our business architecture and how we service your requests.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-wrapper">
    <details class="faq-item" open>
      <summary>How is Playhouse Media Group structured?</summary>
      <div class="faq-content">
        <p>
          Playhouse Media Group (PMG) is a family-run corporate holding company owned by Jacob and
          Youlanda Chademwiri. We manage two distinct flagship service divisions (Apex Web
          Solutions for technology and Tender Edge Solutions for tender compliance) while directly
          running graphic design and SaaS divisions under our central office.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>How do I know which division handles my needs?</summary>
      <div class="faq-content">
        <p>
          Our divisions are strictly specialized. All website design, custom portal development,
          server configuration, domain registrations, and SEO fall under <strong
            >Apex Web Solutions (AWS)</strong
          >. All government bid prep, CSD compliance updates, CIDB gradings, and SBD/MBD documents
          fall under <strong>Tender Edge Solutions (TES)</strong>. Any other needs like custom
          company logo design, corporate profile books, or graphic brand collateral are serviced
          directly by <strong>Playhouse Media Group (PMG)</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can I get branding and web development packages together?</summary>
      <div class="faq-content">
        <p>
          Absolutely! Playhouse Creative Studio will design your corporate logo and brand
          collateral, which Apex Web Solutions will seamlessly integrate into a high-performance
          custom website—all managed smoothly under one parent company.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Where is Playhouse Media Group based?</summary>
      <div class="faq-content">
        <p>
          Our operations are based in <strong
            >Centurion, Pretoria, 0157, Gauteng, South Africa</strong
          >. From this location, we handle direct operations and oversee both local and national
          service pipelines. We also deliver all of our services remotely nationwide.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>
